-1.title: Wyoming Pronghorn
-1.plot: In his home state of Wyoming, Jim Zumbo gives wounded heroes the chance to experience a real western hunt for one of the most unique animals in North America, the pronghorn antelope.

imdb.plot outline: Jim focuses on the realities of hunting, with tips, techniques, & educational information about wildlife habits and behavior. He shows the realities of hunting, rather than just going out and killing an animal, explaining the techniques they're using, and why they're being used in the current situation. He also discusses wildlife habits and behavior and shows how hunters can use that information to their advantage.
